Official sites for test cases

vue js official site for about unit testing -> https://v2.vuejs.org/v2/cookbook/unit-testing-vue-components.html

Vue test utils -> https://v1.test-utils.vuejs.org/

Jest -> https://jestjs.io/

Steps

1) Install vue js and select testing framework like jest, karma and mocha by vue init webpack my-project (for vue cli 2) and also can select e2e with Nightwatch for end to end browser based testing

2) Upgrade chromedriver dependencies if your e2e run is not running, for that whatever chrome browser is installed like for me chromedriver 105.0.0 is perfect.

to upgrade dependecy use command "yarn upgrade chromedriver@105.0.0"

